All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AbstractBaseHandler
This class represents a general handler involving file selection.
CellGridView
This class creates a GridPane of ToggleButtons that is the primary component of the puzzle maker interface.
Main
The driver class that runs the application with given arguments.
NonogramMakerModel
This class contains the functionality of the puzzle maker that is independent of the graphical interface.
NonogramMakerPresenter
The graphical view and model data are connected by this class.
NonogramMakerView
This class creates a BorderPane with a graphical interface for the puzzle maker.
Openable
Interface made to open files.
OpenHandler
Implements the EventHandler interface to the open feature and must implement the handle method this then uses the FileChooser instance variable to show an open dialog to the user.
Saveable
Interface made to save files.
SaveHandler
Implements the EventHandler interface to the save feature and must implement the handle method this then uses the FileChooser instance variable to show an save dialog to the user.
ToggleButtonEventHandler
This class implements the EventHandler interface for the ToggleButtons in CellGridView.
